sentences: The record Thin The Heard was re-released on 12" vinyl in 2017.
In less than a year, the band released their first record Pull The Trigger.
In 2007, they released their second record, Wings Of Angels.
They released their third album, Severed Ties, independently in 2010.
In 2012, O'Brien decided to leave the band to focus more on his family.
In 2014, Brick By Brick started touring.
In 2015, the band signed with Eulogy Recordings and released their first international record, This World, My Enemy.
Records in 2017.
In late 2017, Sean Green had a mutual departure from the band.

In 2018, Brick By Brick signed with Upstate Records, and entered the studio to record their sixth studio record, Hive Mentality, which would include a revamp of the song "In The Ruins", again featuring Vincent Bennett of The Acacia Strain.
